                "@type": "Answer",
                text: "House cleaning in Madison, AL costs $135-$200 for standard cleaning of a typical 3-bedroom home, $225-$350 for deep cleaning, and $275-$450 for move-out cleaning. Madison pricing reflects the area's demand and higher cost of living compared to surrounding counties.",
